---
import { Rocket, ShieldCheck, Zap, Lock } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
            <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-blue-600">
                <Rocket size={24} />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Web-Scale Entropy</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
                Our entropy is sourced from a globally distributed cluster of
                interns rolling high-speed D20 dice in high-altitude data
                centers.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-green-600">
                <ShieldCheck size={24} />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Automatic Deduplication</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
                We check every generated UUID against our master spreadsheet
                (stored in Barnaby's Dropbox) to ensure 0.00000% collisions.
                Guaranteed.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-yellow-500">
                <Zap size={24} />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Post-Quantum Randomness</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
                Our generation algorithm is so random that even we don't know
                what it's doing. Not even Barnaby. Especially not Barnaby.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-purple-600">
                <Lock size={24} />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Enterprise Security</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
                We don't log your UUIDs because we forgot how to setup the
                logging middleware. Your privacy is our technical debt.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 text-center">
        <h4
            class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">
            Trusted by companies that don't know we exist
        </h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-12 grayscale opacity-50">
            <span class="text-2xl font-black">VOIDET</span>
            <span class="text-2xl font-black italic">VibeCheese</span>
            <span class="text-2xl font-black">Placeholder.io</span>
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold">Your Mom's Blog</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
